description:
In episode 626, Jack, Miles, and Jamie are joined by comedian Sara June to discuss Trump questioning the death toll, the CDC report for re-opening businesses, Elon and Grimes' baby name, Dr. Fauci in a romance novel, and more!

  3. Trump and His Infallible Advisers

  5. Big Government Won’t Let Elon Live
  6. IN DR. FAUCI WE STAN
  7. Fauci was model for hero in romance novel by Sally Quinn
  8. Sally Quinn Modeled the Erotic Hero of Her 1991 Bestseller on…Anthony Fauci
  9. Dr. Fauci Inspired a Main Character in a Steamy Bestselling 1991 Romance Novel, Says Author: ‘I Fell in Love With Him’
